spec_data.Name: python3-APScheduler
spec_data.Description:
Advanced Python Scheduler (APScheduler) is a Python library that lets you
schedule your Python code to be executed later, either just once or
periodically.

spec_data.Summary: In-process task scheduler with Cron-like capabilities
